'''杰里米·斯派克·科恩'''（{{lang-en|Jeremy "Spike" Cohen}}，{{bd|1982年|6月28日}}）是一位美国活动家、企业家和播客。他是[[自由意志党|自由意志党]]提名的[[2020年美国总统选举|2020年]][[美国副总统|美国副总统]]候选人，是[[乔·乔根森|乔·乔根森]]的竞选伙伴。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Doherty |first1=Brian |title=Libertarian Party Picks Spike Cohen as Its Vice-Presidential Candidate |url=https://reason.com/2020/05/24/libertarian-party-picks-spike-cohen-as-its-vice-presidential-candidate/ |accessdate=2020-08-25 |publisher=Reason |language=en |date=2020-05-24 |archive-date=2021-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104044539/https://reason.com/2020/05/24/libertarian-party-picks-spike-cohen-as-its-vice-presidential-candidate/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==早年生活==
斯派克·科恩于1982年出生在[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]的[[巴尔的摩|巴尔的摩]]<ref name="Bio" />。科恩的父亲是[[犹太人|犹太人]]，他作为一个{{le|弥赛亚犹太人|Messianic Judaism}}长大，经历了[[犹太教成人礼|犹太教成人礼]]。<ref name="interview">{{cite web |last1=Fox |first1=Blake |title=Interview with Spike Cohen-The Libertarian Party's Jewish VP Nominee |url=https://blogs.timesofisrael.com/interview-with-spike-cohen-the-libertarian-partys-jewish-vp-nominee/ |language=en |date=2020-05-30 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |website=The Times of Israel |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112220423/https://blogs.timesofisrael.com/interview-with-spike-cohen-the-libertarian-partys-jewish-vp-nominee/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

16岁时，科恩开始学习[[网页设计|网页设计]]，随后在几年内建立了一家成功的企业。2016年，33岁的科恩被诊断出患有[[多发性硬化症|多发性硬化症]]。他卖掉了自己的网页设计业务，把注意力转向了[[自由意志主义|自由意志主义]][[行动主义|行动主义]]。科恩是Muddied Waters Media的播客。他称其名字中的“斯派克”来源于1986年的儿童电影《[[小马宝莉：那部电影|小马宝莉：那部电影]]》中的角色斯派克。<ref name="Bio">{{cite web |url=http://verminsupreme2020.com/spike/ |title=Spike Cohen for VP |website=Vermin Supreme 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525184431/http://verminsupreme2020.com/spike/ |accessdate=2020-09-06|archive-date=2020-05-25}}</ref>

==职业生涯==
===2020年副总统竞选===
斯派克·科恩在[[2020年美国总统选举自由意志党初选|2020年自由意志党总统初选]]中，作为总统候选人“[[沃克文·施平|害虫·至上]]”的竞选伙伴参加竞选，并积极参与竞选活动。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ballot-access.org/2020/01/05/two-libertarians-seeking-national-office-campaign-in-libertarian-north-carolina-presidential-primary/ |title=Two Libertarians Seeking National Office Campaign in Libertarian North Carolina Presidential Primary |website=Ballot Access News |last1=Winger |first1=Richard |language=en |date=2020-01-01 |accessdate=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2021-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304215415/http://ballot-access.org/2020/01/05/two-libertarians-seeking-national-office-campaign-in-libertarian-north-carolina-presidential-primary/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://nymag.com/intelligencer/2020/05/libertarians-decide-to-become-a-joke-in-2020.html|title=Libertarians Decide to Become a Joke in 2020|website=New York Intelligencer|last1=Kilgore|language=en|first1=Ed|date=2020-05-27|accessdate=2020-09-06|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212050028/https://nymag.com/intelligencer/2020/05/libertarians-decide-to-become-a-joke-in-2020.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年5月23日，“害虫·至上”在自由意志党总统初选中输给了[[乔·乔根森|乔·乔根森]]，但科恩仍在竞选该党的副总统候选人。乔根森更喜欢{{le|约翰·蒙兹|John Monds}}做她的竞选搭档，而不是科恩和{{le|肯·阿姆斯特朗|Ken Armstrong (politician)}}，但尽管如此，经过三轮投票，科恩还是以533张代表票击败了蒙兹，后者获得了472张选票<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ballot-access.org/2020/05/24/libertarian-party-nominates-spike-cohen-for-vice-president/ |title=Libertarian Party Nominates Spike Cohen for Vice-President |website=Ballot Access News |last1=Winger |first1=Richard |language=en |date=2020-05-24 |accessdate=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308073348/https://ballot-access.org/2020/05/24/libertarian-party-nominates-spike-cohen-for-vice-president/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。作为自由意志党的副总统候选人，科恩成为继[[2000年美国总统选举|2000年美国总统选举]]的[[乔·利伯曼|乔·利伯曼]]之后第一位[[犹太裔|犹太裔]]政党副总统候选人<ref name="interview" />。

==政治立场==
斯派克·科恩声明，他和乔根森的政纲源自[[自由意志党|自由意志党]]的纲领。这包括通过缩小政府规模来减少国家债务、进行广泛的刑事司法改革和立即释放因[[无被害人犯罪|无被害人犯罪]]而被监禁的人、警察非军事化和建立警察问责方案。<ref>{{cite web |author=L.P. Colorado |url=https://lpcolorado.org/2020/06/04/a-message-from-spike-cohen-jo-jorgensens-running-mate/ |title=A Message from Spike Cohen, Jo Jorgensen's Running Mate |date=2020-06-05 |language=en |access-date=2020-09-06 |archive-date=2020-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620142701/https://lpcolorado.org/2020/06/04/a-message-from-spike-cohen-jo-jorgensens-running-mate/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

